    },
    {
        ".  As a technological discipline, computer vision seeks to apply its theories and models for the construction of computer vision systems.       In the late 1960s, computer vision began at universities which were pioneering ": null
    },
    {
        "artificial intelligence": "Artificial Intelligence"
    },
    {
