    },
    {
        " were used to solve ": null
    },
    {
        "image segmentation": "Image Segmentation"
    },
    {
        ". This decade also marked the first time statistical learning techniques were used in practice to recognize faces in images . Toward the end of the 1990s, a significant change came about with the increased interaction between the fields of ": null
    },
    {
